com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util

Class IterableObjectPagination<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util.JsonArrayPagination
      • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util.IterableObjectPagination<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of objects on the pages.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlarmCollection, AuditRecordCollection, BinariesCollection, BulkOperationCollection, EventCollection, ExternalIdCollection, GroupCollection, GroupReferenceCollection, ManagedObjectCollection, MeasurementCollection, ModuleCollection, NewDeviceRequestCollection, OperationCollection, RetentionRuleCollection, RoleCollection, RoleReferenceCollection, UserReferenceCollection

    public class IterableObjectPagination<T>
extends JsonArrayPagination
    Simplifies iteration over paged result by providing access to paged objects via Stream. The object stream can be accessed via stream(). It will read pages *only* if necessary and forward until the end of result (the last page) is reached.
